        <p>Beside its focus on cutting-edge technologies, algorithms and devices, he's also hands-on with <strong>Windows Apps</strong> development, cross-platform mobile apps development with <strong>Xamarin</strong> and the cloud, with projects using <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong> services (Functions, Media Services, apps, big data).</p>
