        <p>He is an active member of the local technology community <a href="http://www.torinotechnologiesgroup.it/" target="_blank" title="TTG - Torino Technologies Group"><strong>TTG - Torino Technologies Group</strong></a> and periodically is a speaker in national and international community events (such as WPC, Community Days, Microsoft Ignite, Droidcon, etc. to name a few).</p>
